    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved. It\u2019s perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. I've kept it nice and clean, and it's totally ready for a new home. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it!",
