      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust example of a mid-engine icon. This Cayman S features the 3.4L flat-six powerplant, delivering linear torque through its 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains its legendary poise with firm damping and precise steering rack feedback. Recent service includes a comprehensive inspection of the cooling system and a fresh set of high-performance tires to minimize unsprung mass. While the exterior shows minor signs of spirited driving, the powertrain remains tight with no signs of bore scoring or IMS issues common in lesser-maintained units. A driver-focused machine optimized for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Regular service history.",
