    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, blending performance with a refined aesthetic. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only the lightest evidence of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a pristine environment; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, resulting in a whisper-quiet engine and a transmission that delivers seamless, confident shifts. With a clean title and a smoke-free history, this car offers a premium driving experience for those who value both style and peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
