    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s honestly such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, dependable ride without any fuss. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next big adventure. Come check it out, I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
