    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit features a recently overhauled double-VANOS system and verified valve clearances, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with precision. The drivetrain includes the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. To address platform-specific concerns, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and the suspension geometry is maintained via fresh bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical integrity is prioritized, featuring a healthy cooling system and consistent compression numbers. A purist\u2019s spec designed for peak lateral grip and linear power delivery.",
